history.content:
Read: http://registrar.berkeley.edu/Records/igrades.html

The assignments you have to complete are supposed to be roughly the assignments you didn't do, which will depend on when you had to take the incomplete; your instructor should tell you.

Please speak to your instructor directly to see what remains to be done. You must set a date by which you will finish any missing work. For any additional questions, please contact me: svannostrand@eecs.berkeley.edu. 

Thanks

I'm not sure what the process for removing that Incomplete is, and does anyone know what kind of assignments I would have to complete to remove it? Would I be retaking the midterms and doing the projects/homework/labs?
